Name: Real Estate Property Listing Portal

Features:
- Property listing with add, edit, delete operations.
- Search across properties (client-side / server-side search).
- Pagination for listing pages to handle large result sets.
- Toast notifications for user feedback (uses react-toastify).
- Responsive UI with property cards and detail views.

Workflow:
- User visits the Home page which shows paginated property listings.
- User can search or filter results; pagination updates accordingly.
- Click a property to view details on the Property Details page.
- Authenticated users (if enabled) can add or edit property details using the Add / Edit pages.
- Client uses Axios to call backend API endpoints; backend persists data in MongoDB via Mongoose.
- Toast notifications show success / error messages on actions.

Technology:
- Backend: Node.js, Express, MongoDB (via Mongoose), dotenv, CORS, Morgan
- Frontend: React, Vite, React Router, Axios, React-Toastify
- Dev tools: nodemon (backend), Vite dev server (frontend)

