Notes:
- Toast notifications are implemented using `react-toastify` in the frontend.
- Pagination and search features are implemented in the frontend components and may call backend endpoints for server-side filtering.

How to run (local development):
1. Backend
   - cd backend
   - npm install
   - copy .env.example to .env and set MONGO_URI (if present)
   - npm run dev

2. Frontend
   - cd frontend
   - npm install
   - npm run dev

